### ValueSet: WB Rolle - $expand
# @name expand
GET http://localhost:8080/ValueSet/wb-rolle/$expand
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

### ValueSet: WB Rolle - $validate-code valid (wb-assistent)
# @name validate_valid_1
GET http://localhost:8080/ValueSet/wb-rolle/$validate-code?system=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/CodeSystem/wb-rolle&code=wb-assistent
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

### ValueSet: WB Rolle - $validate-code valid (sicherstellungsassistent)
